Sentencas: Double perovskite Sr2MnMoO5+delta (SMM) based hybrid catalyst is synthesized with SrMoO4 (SM) nanoparticles' in-situ exsolution.
Titulo: A double perovskite decorated carbon-tolerant redox electrode for symmetrical SOFC

Sentencas: And the super exchange model in double perovskite structure enable the excellent redox property of SMM based electrode.
Titulo: A double perovskite decorated carbon-tolerant redox electrode for symmetrical SOFC

Sentencas: Electrolyte (Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9, SDC)-supported symmetrical solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) is prepared with the structure as SMM/NiO-SDC parallel to SDC parallel to NiO-SDC/SMM.
Titulo: A double perovskite decorated carbon-tolerant redox electrode for symmetrical SOFC

Sentencas: The NiO-SDC powders are prepared from gel-casting combined co-synthetic method and SMM hybrid catalyst is loaded on NiO-SDC scaffold by solution infiltration.
Titulo: A double perovskite decorated carbon-tolerant redox electrode for symmetrical SOFC

Sentencas: In-situ exsolved SM particles provide additional oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) active sites on electrode surface which also contributes to the cell's cathodic performance.
Titulo: A double perovskite decorated carbon-tolerant redox electrode for symmetrical SOFC

Sentencas: The peak power densities of 245 and 183 mW/cm(2) can be achieved by as-prepared electrode when operating in wet CH4 and C2H5OH fuels at 800 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: A double perovskite decorated carbon-tolerant redox electrode for symmetrical SOFC

Sentencas: And the cell runs stably for over 320 h with hydrocarbon fuel, which reveals SMM/NiO-SDC electrode's high electrochemical activity and promising carbon deposition resistance.
Titulo: A double perovskite decorated carbon-tolerant redox electrode for symmetrical SOFC
